description:
Danny is back to recap The Real Housewives of Potomac season 6 premiere! The episode features a box argument between Karen and Gizelle, Mia's debut, a new house for Candiace, and SO much more! The Potomac women are back and better than ever!!!


*To support this pod & access bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
